Introduction

FE:VERSE is a five-member virtual girl group under Kakao Entertainment. They were formed through the survival show GIRL'S RE:VERSE. They debuted on May 9, 2023, with their first mini album Cho.

The members consist of idols from different groups like Eunbi (ex. IZ*ONE), Soobin and Luda (WJSN), Hayoung (Apink), and Heejin (ARTMS).

Their name is about their origin name: GIRL'S RE:VERSE, and is also the abbreviation of fever, ever, and verse, which is formed to mean "passion, forever and universe" respectively.
